This repository is for the KojackGames.Blackjack tutorial in "Pro Agile .NET Development with Scrum" by Jerrel Blankenship, Matthew Bussa and Scott Millett.

This is a work in progress as I complete the referenced book. It will be in various stages of usability and really isn't for public consumption. 

The full source code can be downloaded from APress:
http://www.apress.com/downloadable/download/sample/sample_id/1198/